@startuml
title 审批流程引擎（复杂度 O(n³)）

actor 提交人 as op
actor 审核人 as checker
actor 审批人 as approver
participant "前端" as front
participant "Gateway" as gw
participant "zrws-approval" as svc
participant "bpmn-js 引擎" as bpmn
database "MySQL" as db
queue "RabbitMQ" as mq

== 提交审批 ==
op -> front: 提交审核申请
front -> gw: POST /api/v1/approval/submit
gw -> svc: 转发
svc -> db: [SQL] INSERT t_approval_task
svc -> bpmn: 启动流程实例
bpmn -> svc: 下一节点：审核
svc -> mq: 发送 approval.node.incoming
mq -> svc: 通知审核人

== 审核节点 ==
checker -> front: 查看待办
front -> gw: GET /api/v1/approval/todo
gw -> svc: 查询待办列表
checker -> front: 通过/驳回
front -> gw: PUT /api/v1/approval/{id}/review
gw -> svc: 提交审核意见
svc -> bpmn: 节点完成 → 下一节点
bpmn -> svc: 审批人节点
svc -> mq: 发送 approval.node.incoming

== 审批节点 ==
approver -> front: 查看待办 + 附件
approver -> front: 批准/退回
front -> gw: PUT /api/v1/approval/{id}/approve
gw -> svc: 最终审批
svc -> bpmn: 流程结束
svc -> db: [SQL] UPDATE t_approval_task SET status='APPROVED'
svc -> mq: 发送 approval.finalized

== 异常流程 ==
alt 驳回
    checker -> front: 填写驳回原因
    svc -> bpmn: 退回提交人
    svc -> mq: 发送 approval.returned
    op -> front: 修改后重新提交
else 超时未处理
    svc -> svc: 定时任务扫描 48h 未处理
    svc -> mq: 发送 approval.escalation
    mq -> svc: 通知上级审批人
end

@enduml
